{"code":200,"message":"OK","tweet":{"url":"https://x.com/ai_xiaomu/status/2068613828687085699","id":"2068613828687085699","text":"","raw_text":{"text":"https://t.co/hoYijLzfus","display_text_range":[0,23],"facets":[]},"author":{"screen_name":"ai_xiaomu","url":"https://x.com/ai_xiaomu","id":"885347162233610242","followers":37135,"following":619,"likes":5698,"media_count":1117,"name":"黄小木","description":"💼 大厂年薪百万牛马，26年4月提桶跑路。\n♥️ 来X分享从程序员转型OPC的一切 。\n👨🏻‍💻 写段子｜写教程｜写副业，木哥Opc群&咨询👇。","raw_description":{"text":"💼 大厂年薪百万牛马，26年4月提桶跑路。\n♥️ 来X分享从程序员转型OPC的一切 。\n👨🏻‍💻 写段子｜写教程｜写副业，木哥Opc群&咨询👇。","facets":[]},"location":"深圳","banner_url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/885347162233610242/1775030769","avatar_url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2041273894385164288/IWPvEBQT_200x200.jpg","joined":"Thu Jul 13 03:56:27 +0000 2017","protected":false,"website":{"url":"https://my.feishu.cn/wiki/OLq5wsLUti49vpkctPzcrPKOnme","display_url":"my.feishu.cn/wiki/OLq5wsLUt…"},"verification":{"verified":true,"verified_at":null,"type":"individual"},"avatar_color":null},"replies":76,"retweets":272,"likes":1399,"bookmarks":3325,"quotes":72,"created_at":"Sun Jun 21 08:35:44 +0000 2026","created_timestamp":1782030944,"possibly_sensitive":false,"views":613893,"is_note_tweet":false,"community_note":null,"lang":null,"replying_to":null,"replying_to_status":null,"source":"Twitter Web App","article":{"created_at":"2026-06-21T08:35:44.000Z","modified_at":"2026-06-21T08:35:44.000Z","id":"2068611360217559040","title":"GEO 从 0 到 1 小白完整教程(让AI推荐你的产品)","preview_text":"用户买东西、找工具，越来越多人不再去搜索，而是直接问 豆包，问ChatGPT。\n如果你的产品没出现在 AI 给的答案里，那不管你产品有多好，在这个新入口面前你就是查无此人。\n一篇讲清楚：怎么让 AI 推荐你的产品。","cover_media":{"id":"QXBpTWVkaWE6DAAFCgABHLUvIHHbYAAKAAIMSWKNo9WgAgAA","media_id":"2068611420242272256","media_info":{"__typename":"ApiImage","color_info":{"palette":[{"percentage":46.92,"rgb":{"blue":237,"green":243,"red":250}},{"percentage":46.4,"rgb":{"blue":38,"green":31,"red":28}},{"percentage":1.33,"rgb":{"blue":239,"green":176,"red":190}},{"percentage":0.38,"rgb":{"blue":241,"green":142,"red":158}},{"percentage":0.29,"rgb":{"blue":115,"green":62,"red":39}}]},"original_img_height":793,"original_img_url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HLUvIHHbYAAP_PK.jpg","original_img_width":1983},"media_key":"3_2068611420242272256"},"content":{"blocks":[{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"2p26l","text":"用户买东西、找工具，越来越多人不再去搜索，而是直接问 豆包，问ChatGPT。","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"b4spd","text":"如果你的产品没出现在 AI 给的答案里，那不管你产品有多好，在这个新入口面前你就是查无此人。","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":14,"offset":6,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"7r10r","text":"一篇讲清楚：怎么让 AI 推荐你的产品。","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"fsq8l","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"7julq","text":"第 1 章 GEO 是什么、AI 产品为什么必须做","type":"header-one"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"bjv6","text":"1.1 GEO 是什么","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"dfj9n","text":"GEO（生成式引擎优化，英文 Generative Engine Optimization）：让你的内容能被 AI 看见、读懂、引用，最后被推荐出去。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"1a6oe","text":"跟它对比的是你可能听过的 SEO（搜索引擎优化），两者差在哪，一句话就能说清：","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"fic14","text":"SEO 是让你在搜索结果列表里排名靠前，像在货架上抢个好位置，用户能一眼看到你；","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"98p3d","text":"GEO 是让 AI 在回答问题时，直接报出你的名字，像让一个懂行的导购，主动把你推荐给顾客。","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"cfgvr","text":"举例，用户问 AI： 有哪些好用的 AI 会议记录工具？","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"9ucvq","text":"如果 AI 的回答里直接列出了 NoteFlow(虚拟产品)，还顺带说了它好在哪，这就是 GEO 有效果了。 用户根本没去搜索、没点链接，AI 直接把答案喂到了嘴边。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"90si0","text":"你可能还听过 AEO、AISEO 这些词，其实说的都是一回事，GEO 是目前最通用的叫法。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"k99l","text":"1.2 流量的入口正在变","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"1b6jm","text":"为什么这件事现在突然重要起来？","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"3pqt","text":"因为用户获取信息的方式变了。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"fcs1n","text":"以前你想知道一件事，得去搜索框打关键词，然后在一堆链接里自己挑、自己辨别真假。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"fskni","text":"现在越来越多的人直接问 AI，AI 直接给一个整理好的答案。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"670rh","text":"这就带来一个新现象，叫零点击搜索。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"48jcr","text":"以前你搜明天天气，得点进天气网站看；","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"3vch2","text":"现在你问 AI，它直接告诉你：明天晴，25 度。你看完就走了，没点任何链接。","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"tp9u","text":"对 AI 产品来说，这意味着流量逻辑彻底变了。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"7p575","text":"过去你拼的是搜索排名，现在你要拼的是有没有被 AI 引用。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"3ntoc","text":"谁被 AI 翻牌子，谁就是用户眼里的权威。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"air7u","text":"1.3 为什么 AI 产品尤其该做","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"jf38","text":"GEO 对所有生意都有用，但对做 AI 产品、尤其是做海外市场的人，是一块格外大的机会。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":19,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"1voo8","text":"第一，海外的 AI 和互联网是互通的。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"8scuj","text":"ChatGPT、Perplexity、谷歌 AI 概览这些海外 AI，可以直接通过爬虫抓取全网数据，包括你自己的产品官网。这跟国内数据各自割裂、AI 很难抓到小网站的情况完全不同。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":17,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"93crb","text":"第二，海外 AI 尊重优质的官网。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"5d9sv","text":"在海外，一个内容扎实、结构清晰的产品官网，本身就是 AI 高度信任的信息源。也就是说，你把自己的网站做好，就是做 GEO 最直接、最高效的手段。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":41,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"612af","text":"在国内做 GEO 主要靠大平台借势，在海外做 GEO，你自己的产品官网就是主战场。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"bthno","text":"所以做海外产品的人要有个自己的独立站。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":1,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"7os7k","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"5mhqu","text":"第 2 章 你的 AI 产品适不适合做 GEO","type":"header-one"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"9f89g","text":"GEO 是大趋势，但不是每个生意都值得投入，动手之前先做个判断。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"fu2p9","text":"2.1 什么样的生意适合","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":21,"offset":10,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"87kdj","text":"判断的核心是一句话：用户在掏钱之前，会不会先去问一问、查一查？","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"u8vl","text":"越是需要做功课才下单的生意，GEO 的回报越高。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"1c2b6","text":"三类典型：","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":2,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"9r8sr","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"9a4rj","text":"我们的例子 NoteFlow 属于第一类，卖的是 SaaS 工具，用户买之前一定会到处比较，正是 GEO 的甜区。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"9cnnn","text":"2.2 两个入场条件","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"hf2","text":"不是想做就能做，AI 抓取内容有它的脾气，你必须先具备两个基础条件。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":10,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"4bb5o","text":"第一，手里得有内容。如果你的网站全是空洞口号，没有干货，AI 没东西可抓。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":10,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"9cmof","text":"第二，网上得有痕迹。如果全网只有你自己说自己好，AI 是不会信的。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"39h5f","text":"这里要破除一个老板常有的误区： 以为砸钱投广告就能让 AI 认识自己，在人的世界这逻辑通，在 AI 的世界不通。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"8e4eo","text":"不是你投了广告，AI 就认识你。你必须在互联网上留下索引数据。","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"a73ih","text":"什么叫索引数据？是带第三方视角的真实讨论。 比如一篇测评里写到你产品的优缺点，这是索引数据； 而你自己喊的全宇宙最好用，那只是广告噪音。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"95p8l","text":"如果你的品牌网上只有广告、没有任何真实讨论，AI 会判定你查无此人。 更糟的是，当用户问你靠不靠谱时，AI 因为找不到足够信息，可能直接胡编，甚至把别人的负面信息安到你头上。 所以哪怕不激进推广，也要做最基础的填坑，至少让 AI 知道你是谁。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":3,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"bbvj9","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"bd2b5","text":"第 3 章 AI 凭什么推荐你","type":"header-one"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"f6csb","text":"AI 没有喜怒哀乐，它推荐谁是一套完全机械、可拆解的流程。 ","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"dr4r","text":"搞懂这套机制，你就掌握了 GEO 的核心逻辑。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"ch2j4","text":"3.1 AI 回答问题的两步：检索和生成","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"a8mpj","text":"现在的 AI 搜索，背后普遍用一种叫 RAG（检索增强生成，英文 Retrieval-Augmented Generation）的技术：它就两步。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":7,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"e2tan","text":"第一步，检索。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"6qmco","text":"你一提问，AI 先去它连接的互联网上做一轮搜索，瞬间抓取一批相关内容，可能是新闻、可能是你的官网、可能是某个论坛回答。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":7,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"2avp3","text":"第二步，生成。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"edcm2","text":"AI 读这些抓来的内容，提取核心事实，再用自己的话重新组织，生成最终答案给用户。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"aors4","text":"这里藏着一个重点逻辑：","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"fbfqi","text":"如果你的内容在第一步没被检索到，或者在第二步因为写得太乱没被提取，你的品牌就绝不可能出现在最终答案里。","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"9nv03","text":"换句话说，做 GEO 就是反过来想：AI 是怎么检索、怎么提取的，我就怎么写、怎么发。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"frjkm","text":"3.2 AI 筛选内容的三层漏斗","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"84qjt","text":"在全网那么多网页里，AI 凭什么选中你？","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"61c3u","text":"可以理解成一个三层漏斗，一层层往下筛。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":14,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"3p5an","text":"第一层，能看见（可检索性）。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"1b4ai","text":"这是物理门槛，AI 首先得能找到你。它倾向抓高权重信源，对你的产品官网来说，如果技术设置屏蔽了 AI 爬虫，或者网页慢得要死，AI 直接放弃。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":14,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"8h77l","text":"第二层，读得懂（可理解性）。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"avft4","text":"AI 抓到内容后要做语义分析，它喜欢结构清晰、信息密度高的东西。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"4svfh","text":"AI 讨厌：情绪化的软文、逻辑混乱的长篇、全是形容词的广告语。","type":"unordered-list-item"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"6hsos","text":"AI 喜欢：定义清晰、列表明确、参数量化的内容，一读就懂，提取效率高。","type":"unordered-list-item"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":13,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"fpvtf","text":"第三层，信得过（可信度）。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"d38h5","text":"这是 AI 防止自己胡说的机制，它会优先引用看起来有据可依的内容。 这里的关键词是交叉验证：单一来源权重低，但如果你的官网说、测评说、新闻也说，AI 就判定这事可信。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"1peh2","text":"3.3 GEO 的核心公式","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"bjmdj","text":"把上面的机制总结成一个好记的公式，GEO 其实就等于 SEO 加 RAG：","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"8lu5a","text":"GEO = SEO（让 AI 搜得到你）+ RAG（让 AI 愿意引用你）","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"bp3ot","text":"可展开成可操作的三件事：","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"1dueq","text":"高推荐率 = 权威渠道（找得到）+ 结构化内容（读得懂）+ 数据背书（信得过）","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":4,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"870li","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"c5v48","text":"第 4 章 怎么写 AI 愿意引用的内容","type":"header-one"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"bf2ru","text":"AI 不懂文学，也没审美，在它眼里文章没有优美和枯燥之分，只有结构清晰和逻辑混乱的区别。 它抓内容的时候，本质是在做填空题。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":9,"offset":20,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"cjm36","text":"所以写 GEO 内容的黄金法则只有一条：写有结构的说明书。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"7ctnu","text":"4.1 写作总原则：结论前置","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"c98cv","text":"传统文章喜欢起承转合，把核心观点藏在最后。 ","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"1drrs","text":"这对 AI 是灾难，它读到一半抓不到重点就放弃了。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"3lg7","text":"做 GEO，每一段开头必须先把结论抛出来。 ","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"ebaiu","text":"能用句号别用逗号，能分段别写长句，能用序号别用文字。 目标是让 AI 扫一眼就提取出它要的信息。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"el68q","text":"对比一下同一个产品介绍的两种写法：","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":5,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"demr8","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"8r972","text":"4.2 四个内容模板","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"4rci","text":"根据 AI 对结构化数据的偏好，下面四个模板是最容易被引用的格式。 ","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"e5ie1","text":"建议在同一篇文章里组合使用。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":7,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"c10tr","text":"模板一：定义式（抢占\"是什么\"的解释权）","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"6de1d","text":"AI 回答名词解释类问题时，最爱抓这种句式。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":3,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"ei0fb","text":"公式：","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":6,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"7j4tr","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":3,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"531ca","text":"例子：","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"aad7t","text":"NoteFlow 是一款面向跨国远程团队的 AI 会议记录工具，核心特色是支持 30 种语言混说实时转写，2023 年上线，已服务 5000 多家企业。","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"cdece","text":"当用户问\"NoteFlow 是什么\"时，AI 会直接把这句话当简介搬走。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":7,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"2gj8u","text":"模板二：要点式（抢占\"有哪些\"的总结权）","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"3j10b","text":"AI 不会从头读到尾，它是扫信息的。 列表、编号能让它快速抓住重点，这是它最爱的格式，因为不用重新归纳就能直接复制。 ","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"eqomu","text":"公式：核心观点加冒号，再 1、2、3 分点。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"e26b7","text":"NoteFlow 的三大核心优势：","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"25ul3","text":"1. 多语言：支持 30 种语言混说场景，识别准确率 98%；","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"frd7s","text":"2. 自动化：会议结束 1 分钟内生成纪要和待办清单；","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"7c50o","text":"3. 集成强：可无缝对接 Slack、Notion 等 8 大主流工具。","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":7,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"llms","text":"模板三：结论式（给 AI 一个锚点）","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"3ddtk","text":"AI 生成答案时，会优先选带结论信号的句子。像\"本质上\"\"关键在于\"\"因此\"\"最终意味着\"这种词，能帮模型判断这是一句总结、是答案，而不是描述。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"1lht8","text":"建议每段最后一句写成结论句，比如：","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"13qve","text":"因此，对于需要处理多语言会议的跨国团队来说，NoteFlow 是目前准确率和效率最优的选择。","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":9,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"en94t","text":"模板四：表格对比式（抢占\"哪个好\"的决策权，最好用）","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"2q3oq","text":"这是 GEO 里的核武器。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"11o8s","text":"AI 处理对比类问题时极度依赖表格。 ","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"f62no","text":"你可以做一个我方对竞品的参数对比表，一定要有明确的表头。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":7,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"dfd2c","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"36an6","text":"当用户问\"NoteFlow 和某某工具哪个好\"时，AI 会优先读这张表，直接得出结论。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"707nu","text":"4.3 三个提升信任度的钩子","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"5dfd2","text":"光有结构还不够，还得让 AI 觉得你可信。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"8vfns","text":"在文章里埋三个钩子。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":10,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"badel","text":"第一，多用量化数据。把\"很多、很快、很好\"全换成数字。 ","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"feqfj","text":"AI 对数字极其敏感，它认为数字代表精确和事实。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"5rkfn","text":"错误：好评如潮，速度很快，还省钱。","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"bdo9","text":"正确：好评率 98%，会后 1 分钟生成，节省 60% 整理时间。","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":10,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"5nisc","text":"第二，引用权威信源。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"5crsh","text":"在文中提第三方背书，证明不是自吹。 ","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"2a2ge","text":"比如\"根据某行业报告显示\"\"符合某安全认证标准\"。 ","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"uqn4","text":"AI 会去全网交叉验证，一旦发现有权威机构也这么说，就认定为真。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":10,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"20l75","text":"第三，亮出专家身份。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"f2q0b","text":"文章开头或结尾给作者介绍，越具体越好，比如\"作者：某某，10 年远程协作产品经验\"。 ","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"6negg","text":"AI 很看重\"谁说的\"，署了专家名，权重直接拉满。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"8ossc","text":"4.4 四条写作红线","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"dc8q9","text":"违反任何一条，AI 都可能拒收你的内容。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":8,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"3tu7h","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":19,"offset":5,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"1dori","text":"本章重点：真实加结构，是 GEO 内容的两条命。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":9,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"5d5n8","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"9mu7a","text":"第 5 章 建个独立站","type":"header-one"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"6vd41","text":"5.1 先把站建起来","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"ep4ps","text":"现在你利用codex，一天就能搭出一个像样的网站。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"fkd1b","text":"两个参考示例，按生意类型选：","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":10,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"c9d3t","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"fcrlp","text":"具体怎么搭，去视频网站搜\"Shopify 新手教程\"或\"WordPress 建站教程\"跟着做就行，这里不展开。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"b166v","text":"建好站之后，做 GEO 的第一步是内容得有干货。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"97jp6","text":"别只在官网发公司新闻和团建照片，专门开一个博客版块，发行业白皮书、操作教程、完整的产品参数表。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"563sj","text":"这些结构化、信息量大的内容，最容易被 AI 抓走当信息源。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"a8kna","text":"5.2 给网页加一张\"说明书\"：Schema","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"77t26","text":"光有内容还不够，你得用机器能懂的语言告诉 AI 每段内容是什么。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"3f1ht","text":"这就要用到 Schema（结构化数据）。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"bi4gk","text":"Schema 是一套机器通用语言，相当于给网页里的每个信息贴标签：这串数字是价格，那行文字是评分，这个词是库存状态。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"dkpe2","text":"加了这张说明书的页面，被 AI 准确引用的概率会大幅提升。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"5l41s","text":"它写在网页代码里，常见有三类。第一类是产品（Product），告诉 AI 价格、评分、库存：","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":11,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"a4i6q","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"6f8fu","text":"第二类是文章（Article），告诉 AI 这是正经文章、作者是谁、什么时候发的：","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":12,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"2oc1u","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"ac53s","text":"第三类是本地商家（LocalBusiness），告诉 AI 店铺地址、电话，适合有实体的生意。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"5r2mk","text":"结构和上面类似，把类型换成 LocalBusiness，填上地址和电话即可。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"ei8t2","text":"这一步通常需要技术人员加进网页代码，但你知道要加什么、为什么加，就不会被忽悠。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"1qs3n","text":"5.3 把网站大门给 AI 打开","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"bsfiv","text":"很多网站默认是拦爬虫的。你得检查一个叫 robots.txt 的文件，它相当于网站门卫名单，规定谁能进、谁不能进。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"19j9n","text":"做 GEO，千万别把 AI 的爬虫挡在门外。最常见的几个 AI 爬虫名字你要认识：","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":13,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"eo04g","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"dakt8","text":"下面这种写法是错的，它把所有爬虫包括 AI 全挡了：","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":14,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"cc07q","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"e8to2","text":"正确的做法是只挡你想挡的坏爬虫，给 AI 放行，比如：","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":15,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"d94fq","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"6np6o","text":"5.4 给 AI 递一份目录：llms.txt","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"1ib32","text":"还有一个新东西叫 llms.txt，它的作用类似传统 SEO 里的网站地图（sitemap），专门给 AI 看，相当于把你网站的结构整理成一份目录递给 AI，方便它快速理解你有哪些内容。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"3ia3o","text":"好消息是，现在不少建站工具会自动帮你生成 llms.txt，你不用手动配置。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"2ouc3","text":"可以在你的网址后面加上 /llms.txt 看看有没有。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"5ej8k","text":"5.5 顺手做对的两个写作格式","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"3207i","text":"最后两个小习惯，写文档和落地页时顺手做了，对 AI 抓取帮助很大。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":5,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"9dn1n","text":"答案前置。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"7ipfi","text":"每个小节，把最重要的信息放最前面。用户问 AI 要的是直接答案，别在重点前面铺垫三段。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":7,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"17q5h","text":"标题写成问句。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"9roms","text":"把小标题写成用户真会问的问题，而不是抽象名词。因为 AI 会拿用户的提问去匹配你的标题。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"4l4dc","text":"较弱的写法：会议记录功能说明","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"ejojv","text":"更好的写法：NoteFlow 怎么自动生成会议纪要？","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"c2486","text":"这两个习惯不用额外成本，纯粹是写法上的调整，但能实实在在提高被引用的概率。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":16,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"1b3mi","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"637hm","text":"第 6 章 内容怎么布局和找选题","type":"header-one"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"epld4","text":"会写、会铺技术地基了，这一章讲两件事：发什么类型的页面，以及怎么找到该写的选题。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"2unlk","text":"6.1 三类最该做的页面","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"9dtlg","text":"AI 搜索里，用户高频问三类问题，你就用三类页面去对应。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":17,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"8rq02","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"f7qam","text":"对 NoteFlow 来说，就该做这样三组页面： 一组叫\"2026 年最佳 AI 会议记录工具对比\"的榜单页，一组叫\"如何记录多语言跨国会议\"的功能落地页，一组叫\"远程团队会议纪要怎么写\"的教程页。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"c8kd1","text":"6.2 怎么找选题：盯住下拉词","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"e2maj","text":"别拍脑袋想选题。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"3n97k","text":"你以为用户关心产品理念，其实用户关心的可能是另一回事。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"b104s","text":"最笨也最管用的办法，是看搜索框的下拉推荐词。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"4ks75","text":"打开谷歌或者你目标用户常用的平台，输入你的行业核心词，先别按搜索，盯着自动弹出来的下拉列表看。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"ehifa","text":"这些下拉词是海量真实用户搜出来的，也正是 AI 最常被问到的问题。回答这些问题，就是在截最精准的流量。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"etiqu","text":"比如输入 AI meeting notes，下拉弹出 AI meeting notes free、AI meeting notes multilingual，你就知道用户在意免费和多语言，选题就有了。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"brh6b","text":"6.3 软植入关键词","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"867cq","text":"植入品牌时记住两点。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"ea7bf","text":"第一，不要硬广，顺着逻辑植入。 ","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"3ngve","text":"先讲清楚问题和通用解决方案，再自然地举到你的产品。 ","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"8i1iu","text":"比如先科普多语言会议为什么难记录，再说\"以 NoteFlow 为例，它用的是……\"。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"eslsm","text":"第二，关键词密度要克制。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"fosfc","text":"别像老式 SEO 那样疯狂堆词，现在的 AI 没那么傻。 ","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"bju73","text":"你只要确保品牌名在开头（定义）、中间（列表）、结尾（总结）自然出现一次就够，全文三次左右，AI 既记得住你，又不觉得你在灌水。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"dedhl","text":"还有一个玩法叫程序化 GEO，简单说就是用模板加数据批量生成成千上万个长尾页面，覆盖海量细分搜索，当然这条路在315已经被堵死了。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":18,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"1c79a","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"d5osi","text":"第 7 章 判断AI 真的推荐你了","type":"header-one"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"3gp6m","text":"内容发出去只是开始。做 GEO 跟做公众号不一样，你看不到阅读量、点赞数。 你唯一能做的，是模拟真实用户去问 AI，看它嘴里吐不吐出你的名字。 这一步是 GEO 最关键的环节。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"d5l1j","text":"7.1 人工测试三步走","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"36vf7","text":"内容发出去 3 到 7 天后，就可以开始考 AI 了。 把你收集的那些用户提问，拿去 ChatGPT、Perplexity、豆包上挨个问，由浅入深三步。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":17,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"f83g6","text":"第一步，查收录（AI 认识你吗）。直接问：介绍一下 NoteFlow。 如果 AI 能准确说出你是干嘛的，说明它收录了你。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":18,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"1fht1","text":"第二步，查推荐（AI 认可你吗）。  问行业通用词、不带品牌名：推荐几款多语言 AI 会议记录工具。看回答里有没有你。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":9,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"6t3v9","text":"第三步，看引用源。留意 AI 的答案是从哪些页面引来的，这是最值钱的信息。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"dte0v","text":"7.2 没被推荐怎么补救","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"4hnpt","text":"如果AI 推荐的是竞品，两招反击。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":9,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"cmosg","text":"第一招，写对比文。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"bn119","text":"既然 AI 喜欢那个竞品，你就写一篇你和它的对比文，套第 4 章的表格对比模板，突出你的优势。 ","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"66nrm","text":"下次 AI 检索竞品或这个品类时，这篇对比文极可能被抓到，AI 就会说\"虽然某某不错，但如果你更看重多语言，NoteFlow 可能更好\"。 ","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"11s2o","text":"只要同框，你就赢了一半。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":9,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"1otjn","text":"第二招，抢细分词。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"d8p4q","text":"大词竞争太激烈，就抢长尾。 ","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"7ngp3","text":"打不过\"AI 会议记录工具\"，就主攻\"跨国团队多语言会议记录工具\"。 ","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"69e0a","text":"在大池子里争不过，就在小池子里做第一，相关度最高的人会被优先推荐。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"5kaes","text":"7.3 看三个核心指标","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"1uv23","text":"测的时候别只看热闹，盯三个指标，它们决定你下一步的方向怎么走。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":19,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"e4ajd","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"emqpk","text":"如果你要监控的词很多，可以用自动化工具代替人肉去搜，原理一样，只是把重复劳动交给程序。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":5,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"be2gl","text":"本章重点：GEO 是动态博弈，效果监控不能停。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"5prn9","text":"** 你停下维护，竞争对手补内容，AI 的推荐位就会被抢走。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"1ldul","text":"热门行业要保持每周一看，发现掉榜立刻补。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":20,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"11rqf","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"e16cd","text":"第 8 章 避坑与未来","type":"header-one"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"4t0n7","text":"8.1 三条不能碰的红线","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"8jt40","text":"做过 SEO 的人爱用作弊手段，但 GEO 时代别这么干，AI 的审核比搜索引擎更狠，它直接读代码、读语义。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"6dji1","text":"踩了下面三条，轻则降权，重则被永久拉黑。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":8,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"cr47q","text":"隐藏文本堆关键词：把字设成白色藏进背景骗机器，AI 直接读源代码，一眼识破，判你恶意操纵。","type":"unordered-list-item"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":4,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"964ch","text":"数据造假：凭空捏造市场占有率、获奖经历。AI 全网交叉验证，比对不上就给你打低可信标签，以后说真话也不引用。","type":"unordered-list-item"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":7,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"6e1j3","text":"信息太少致幻觉：你太低调、网上信息太少，AI 找不到资料时会自己瞎拼，可能把别人的负面安到你头上。对策是至少在官网和主流渠道留一份准确的官方介绍。","type":"unordered-list-item"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"6c96a","text":"8.2 可提前布局的机会","type":"header-two"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":7,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"flesm","text":"多模态 GEO：AI 正在从读字变成看图。从现在起把网站图片规范命名（别用一串乱码文件名），并加上文字说明（Alt 标签），以后 AI 搜图时这就是它的指路牌。","type":"unordered-list-item"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":5,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"bi9nr","text":"个人 IP：AI 越来越愿意给具体的人更高权重，而不是冷冰冰的公司。把创始人、技术负责人推到台前，在专业文章里强化\"某某认为\"，等 AI 把这个人认成行业权威，他名下的观点权重都会很高。","type":"unordered-list-item"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":21,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"37ete","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"6cddd","text":"写在最后","type":"header-one"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":25,"offset":13,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"eaevl","text":"GEO 核心逻辑就一句话：把你的产品，翻译成机器好索引的语言，让用户能看见。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"2pum1","text":"现在的 GEO 赛道，还没那么卷。此时动手，还能吃到一波红利；等竞争对手的信息都被 AI 充分收录了，再想挤进去，成本会指数级上升，所以尽快动手。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"cg2t1","text":"","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{"mentions":[{"fromIndex":62,"text":"ai_xiaomu","toIndex":72}]},"entityRanges":[{"key":22,"length":10,"offset":62}],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":62,"offset":0,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"2p6r8","text":"黄小木｜T11级工程师｜内容为codex辅助创作，若有侵权请指出｜持续分享 AI 信息、副业赚钱、程序员转型OPC心得｜X：@ai_xiaomu","type":"unstyled"}],"entityMap":[{"key":"12","value":{"data":{"markdown":"```json\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n  \"@type\": \"Article\",\n  \"headline\": \"2026 年最佳 AI 会议记录工具对比\",\n  \"datePublished\": \"2026-06-20\",\n  \"author\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Person\",\n    \"name\": \"张三\"\n  }\n}\n```"},"mutability":"Mutable","type":"MARKDOWN"}},{"key":"8","value":{"data":{"entityKey":"a987fb16-802f-4ac2-a6f7-8e74e790a1ff","mediaItems":[{"localMediaId":"24","mediaCategory":"DraftTweetImage","mediaId":"2068611555282006016"}]},"mutability":"Immutable","type":"MEDIA"}},{"key":"19","value":{"data":{"entityKey":"7f27ceac-2f26-472f-a1b6-a158c34a0d89","mediaItems":[{"localMediaId":"26","mediaCategory":"DraftTweetImage","mediaId":"2068611565436411904"}]},"mutability":"Immutable","type":"MEDIA"}},{"key":"4","value":{"data":{},"mutability":"Immutable","type":"DIVIDER"}},{"key":"15","value":{"data":{"markdown":"```text\nUser-agent: BadBot\nDisallow: /\n\nUser-agent: *\nDisallow: /private/\n```"},"mutability":"Mutable","type":"MARKDOWN"}},{"key":"11","value":{"data":{"markdown":"```json\n{\n